      • getAddress

        java.lang.String getAddress()
        Hyperlink address. Depending on the hyperlink type it can be URL, e-mail, path to a file, etc.(超链接地址。根据超链接类型，它可以是URL、电子邮件、文件路径等。)
        Returns:
        the address of this hyperlink(此超链接的地址)
